<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>网络与新媒体专业课程导航系统</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .main-content {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .intro {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .intro h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .intro p {
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .demo-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .demo-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .demo-button:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .tech-stack {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .tech-stack h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .tech-items {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .tech-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-card h4 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>网络与新媒体专业课程导航系统</h1>
            <p>一个专业的课程管理和学习路径规划工具</p>
        </div>

        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="intro">
                <h2>项目简介</h2>
                <p>本系统是为网络与新媒体专业学生设计的课程导航平台，旨在帮助学生更好地了解专业课程体系、规划学习路径。系统从官方培养方案文档中提取课程信息，提供直观的可视化界面和强大的筛选功能。</p>
                <p>通过本系统，学生可以清晰地查看所有必修课和选修课的分布情况，了解课程之间的先修关系，合理规划每个学期的课程安排。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h4>50+</h4>
                    <p>专业课程</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h4>160+</h4>
                    <p>总学分</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h4>4年</h4>
                    <p>培养周期</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <h4>8个</h4>
                    <p>学期规划</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>📚 课程展示</h3>
                    <p>以卡片和列表形式展示所有课程信息，包括课程代码、名称、学分、学时等详细数据。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>🔍 多维筛选</h3>
                    <p>支持按课程类型（必修/选修）、学分范围、开课学期等多个维度进行筛选。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>📊 学期视图</h3>
                    <p>按学期展示课程分布，帮助学生了解每个学期的课程安排和学习强度。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>📈 统计分析</h3>
                    <p>提供课程总数、总学分、各类型课程占比等统计数据，全面了解专业结构。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>🔎 智能搜索</h3>
                    <p>快速搜索功能，支持按课程名称、代码进行模糊搜索，快速定位目标课程。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>📱 响应式设计</h3>
                    <p>完美适配桌面端和移动端设备，随时随地查看课程信息。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="demo-section">
                <h2>体验系统功能</h2>
                <a href="app/index.html" class="demo-button">进入课程导航系统</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/icgma/new-media-curriculum-navigator" class="demo-button" target="_blank">查看源代码</a>
            </div>

            <div class="tech-stack">
                <h3>技术栈</h3>
                <div class="tech-items">
                    <div class="tech-item">HTML5</div>
                    <div class="tech-item">CSS3</div>
                    <div class="tech-item">JavaScript (ES6+)</div>
                    <div class="tech-item">Python 3.x</div>
                    <div class="tech-item">BeautifulSoup</div>
                    <div class="tech-item">JSON</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>本系统由网络与新媒体专业开发维护 | <a href="https://github.com/icgma/new-media-curriculum-navigator" target="_blank">GitHub</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>